{"tid":1443994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"超勇武手足係咪比犬拉晒啦。。","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:26:11.000Z","uid":280717,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"375bfaeed0e2fe5a54fe4e76fb716d1b4d774a92","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"絕非打擊士氣！<br />\n但問題嚴重！！<br />\n<br />\n近半個月嘅前線絕對有勇氣<br />\n係有勇氣嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係相比以前好似小咗武？<br />\n以前嘅前線會用行山杖攻<br />\n一係直接推返轉頭<br />\n一係救返前面手足<br />\n相比之一近期剩返黃大仙一役<br />\n<br />\n真心想問下....<br />\n係前線手足改咗作戰模式<br />\n定係嗰班超勇武冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外幫手入嚟討論下推下&darr;&darr;<br />\n［香港人一條心］全部人入晒嚟！！遊行 死線 大作戰！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439794</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d01c1eb80f8db919437003060990e386fbc20fe","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5ecc0a213b292d1248b368c520770fcb392acc4f","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82abf56a10406a32598dc97785d2624cf8504f53","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"636209da8dcec0a25121924d4ad0c950a9d77382","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb2fcb97e2a8cf1eb018188e38130e28e65a6b51","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f4d40b12b75ebd14f454451164d559fcff6a6f5","tid":1443994,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5baa296ab41b7cb8ab419f4faeae0d5af2c5